Another challenge

Round 5 reward challenge.

Type: Tribe Reward Challenge

A literal jungle gym — bars suspended in the jungle canopy. Two teams, each with their own set of bars.

The full length of the jungle gym doesn't have enough bars to get across, so players will have to move them as they go. The bars are loosely placed on top of the rails, with loops to keep them in place, but players can slide them out of the loops and move them forward into the next row of loops.

There are a couple checkpoints where players can stand and catch their breath.

The teams all start on a platform, and they all have to get across. Players decide how to move the bars, and which team members will help move the bars, etc.

If anyone falls off the bars, the players need to go back to the last checkpoint (including the players currently on the bars).
